{"_id":"5uH81I1GFIjYhSvC","name":"Where are you going all alone, sweetie?","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-scenario-gift-Where are you going all alone, sweetie?-2","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"¿A dónde vas tan sola, dulzura?","system":{"description":"<h3>Requisito</h3><p>Encontrarte con Iskra a solas en el bosque.</p><h3>Efecto</h3><p>Te sientes atraído por la pequeña que finge ser una loba y sueñas con devorarla. Una vez por escena, puedes gastar 1 Soma para saber exactamente dónde está. Si te anticipas a ella y llegas antes a un lugar, obtienes 1 Éxito adicional en cada prueba que hagas para herirla o devorarla. No puedes esperar para tragar ese bocado, y eso te hace bajar la guardia: mientras ella esté presente en la escena, recibes 1 Penalización en todas tus pruebas de Defensa.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Requirement</h3><p>To meet Iskra alone in the forest.</p><h3>Effect</h3><p>You are attracted to the little girl who pretends to be a wolf and you dream of devouring her. Once per Scene, you can spend 1 Soma to know exactly where she is. If you anticipate her and arrive somewhere before her, you get 1 Additional Success on every Check you make to hurt or devour that little morsel. You can’t wait to swallow that tidbit and it makes you let your guard down. As long as she is present in the Scene, you receive 1 Penalty in all Defense Checks.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift. Legacy Iskra adventure support from local backups.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","successes":0,"source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242149,"modifiedTime":1783973242149,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8nq1cZqBkf27sNQP","name":"Iskra's Pendant","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/jewelry/necklace-pendant-moon-silver.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Iskra's Pendant-3","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Colgante de Iskra","system":{"description":"<p>Un viejo colgante de barro que Iskra hizo una vez para su madre como regalo: el recuerdo de un raro momento de felicidad. Elizaveta intentó deshacerse de él arrojándolo al viejo pozo del cementerio, pero todavía puede encontrarse en el fondo. Es tosco, hecho a mano, pero conmovedor: muestra el amor inocente de una niña por su madre.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>An old earthenware pendant that Iskra once made for her mother as a gift, a memento of a rare moment of happiness. Elizaveta tried to dispose of it by throwing it into the old well at the cemetery, but it can still be found at the bottom of the well. This handmade pendant is crude but touching, showing the innocent love of a child for her mother.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Iskras Pendant.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MVIBG1whitQLiPcj","name":"Iskra's Wolf Mask","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/equipment/head/mask-carved-wood-tan.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Iskra's Wolf Mask-5","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Máscara de lobo de Iskra","system":{"description":"<p>Una máscara rudimentaria de madera tallada por la propia Iskra para ocultar su rostro. Representa rasgos de lobo y le sirve tanto para esconder su identidad como para expresar su naturaleza adoptada como parte de la manada de Greskar.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>A rudimentary wooden mask carved by Iskra's own hands to hide her face. The mask depicts a wolf's features and serves both to conceal her identity and to express her adopted nature as part of Greskar's wolf pack. The craftsmanship is crude but effective, showing her adaptation to survival in the wild.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Iskras Wolf Mask.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SlUDkRybsTid8vuj","name":"Gerard's Letter to the Papacy","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/scrolls/scroll-worn-tan-brown.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Gerard's Letter to the Papacy-2","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Carta de Gerard al Papado","system":{"description":"<p>Una carta escrita con la mano temblorosa de lord Gerard Dubois y enviada al Papado para suplicar ayuda. La carta dice: “Las bestias que amenazan al Gévaudan son antinaturales, creadas por algo que no es Dios”. Esta petición desesperada llevó a los Cazadores de la Orden a Durfort.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>A letter written in Lord Gerard Dubois' trembling hand, sent to the Papacy begging for help. The letter reads: 'The beasts that menace the Gévaudan are unnatural, fashioned by something other than God.' This desperate plea brought the Order's Hunters to Durfort.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Gerards Letter to the Papacy.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"XWTcN87Yf8hSBix2","name":"Iskra's Red Cape","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/equipment/back/cloak-layered-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Iskra's Red Cape-4","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Capa roja de Iskra","system":{"description":"<p>Una capa roja raída, el último regalo de la madre de Iskra antes de enviar a su hija a una supuesta muerte en el bosque. Iskra todavía la lleva como recuerdo y como símbolo de su venganza. La capa está manchada de barro y sangre por su vida entre lobos.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>A threadbare red cape, the last gift from Iskra's mother before she sent her daughter to her supposed death in the forest. Despite its worn condition, Iskra still wears it as both a memory and a symbol of her quest for revenge. The cape is stained with mud and blood from her time living as a wolf.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Iskras Red Cape.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YlSZepEr8hex0vWv","name":"Voice of the Spirits","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-scenario-gift-Voice of the Spirits-0","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Voz de los espíritus","system":{"description":"<h3>Requisito</h3><p>Haber entrado en contacto con el Don Espíritu.</p><h3>Efecto</h3><p>Calmando tu mente y concentrándote, puedes abrirte al mundo espiritual y comunicarte con almas inquietas. Gasta 1 Soma para contactar con una criatura con el Don Espíritu que hayas encontrado previamente. No sufres la Herida causada por el estrés de la conexión espiritual.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Requirement</h3><p>You have come into contact with the Gift Spirit.</p><h3>Effect</h3><p>By calming your mind and concentrating, you can open your mind to the spiritual world and communicate with restless souls. Spend 1 Soma to contact a creature with the Spirit Gift you’ve previously encountered. You do not suffer the Wound caused by the stress of spiritual connection.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift. Legacy Iskra adventure support from local backups.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","successes":0,"source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242149,"modifiedTime":1783973242149,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bSl4tyl4BOFiHYxU","name":"Elizaveta's Poison","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-purple.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Elizaveta's Poison-1","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Veneno de Elizaveta","system":{"description":"<p>Una preparación venenosa usada por Elizaveta para mover sus piezas con discreción y librarse de quienes amenazan su posición.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>A powerful poison that Elizaveta keeps hidden in the palace. If Iskra is captured, Elizaveta will attempt to use this poison to eliminate her unwanted daughter once and for all. The poison is potent enough to kill even someone with supernatural resilience.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Elizavetas Poison.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"dgboL8H0LEHkDGLy","name":"Blood Drawings in the Den","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/documents/document-torn-brown-red.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Blood Drawings in the Den-0","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Dibujos de sangre en la guarida","system":{"description":"<p>Marcas y dibujos trazados con sangre en la guarida de los lobos, rastros de la furia de Iskra y de su vínculo con la manada.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>Crude drawings on the cave walls of the wolves' den, depicting a mother and daughter holding hands. They are drawn in blood, a haunting testament to Iskra's lost innocence and her desperate longing for the maternal love she was denied. These drawings reveal the tragic humanity still present within the wolf-girl.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Blood Drawings in the Den.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242149,"modifiedTime":1783973242149,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hCfQ34jKjClyL0zo","name":"Portrait of Patrick Dubois","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/misc/portrait-painting-frame.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Portrait of Patrick Dubois-6","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Retrato de Patrick Dubois","system":{"description":"<p>Un retrato solemne de Patrick Dubois, padre de Gerard. Su presencia todavía pesa sobre la familia y sobre los salones del palacio.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>An enormous painting of Patrick Dubois, Gerard's late father, hanging in the ceremonial hall. The portrait shows a stern and sullen-looking man who seems to judge his son's incompetence from beyond the grave with ill-concealed contempt. Every room in the palace is filled with flattering paintings of Patrick, a constant reminder of Gerard's inadequacy.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Portrait of Patrick Dubois.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242150,"modifiedTime":1783973242150,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"nsLwnAjKz27oRwbS","name":"Wolf-killer","type":"gift","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/icon-gift.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-scenario-gift-Wolf-killer-1","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Matalobos","system":{"description":"<h3>Requisito</h3><p>Haber enfrentado a los lobos en combate al menos una vez.</p><h3>Efecto</h3><p>Sabes cómo tratar con los lobos más feroces y tienes cuidado de no quedar rodeado. Cuando obtienes al menos un Resultado estándar en una prueba de Posición o Defensa contra una manada de bestias, puedes eliminar inmediatamente 1 PNJ animal menor con 1 Herida.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Requirement</h3><p>Having faced the wolves in a fight at least once.</p><h3>Effect</h3><p>You know how to deal with the fiercest of wolves and are careful not to be surrounded. When you obtain at least a Standard Outcome on a Position or Defense Check against a pack of beasts, you can immediately eliminate 1 Minor animal NPC with 1 Wound.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift. Legacy Iskra adventure support from local backups.","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","successes":0,"source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242149,"modifiedTime":1783973242149,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"p4b4rMBWtEtyPCbc","name":"Wolf Tracks and Child's Footprints","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/misc/paw-print.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"legacySource":"Recovered legacy source","importSlug":"iskra-story-element-Wolf Tracks and Child's Footprints-7","scenarioSlug":"general","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","folderName":"General","sourceDirectory":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Huellas de lobo y pisadas de niña","system":{"description":"<p>Un rastro inquietante donde las huellas de lobo se mezclan con pequeñas pisadas humanas, una pista clara de la doble naturaleza de Iskra.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"system":{"description":"<p>In the old cemetery, there are many wolf tracks scattered throughout the grounds. Hidden among them are the prints of two small bare feet, almost certainly belonging to a little girl. These tracks lead deep into the Gévaudan forest, toward the wolves' den. This evidence suggests that a child is somehow involved with the wolf pack.</p>","notes":"Red-Hood Iskra adventure element. Legacy file: Wolf Tracks and Childs Footprints.json.","category":"Scenario Support","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"general","source":"Red-Hood Iskra"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973242151,"modifiedTime":1783973242151,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"name":"Pile of Bones and Corpses","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/commodities/bones/bones-skull-white.webp","system":{"description":"<p>A large cave in the wolves' lair filled with bones and human corpses - the grim remains of the pack's victims. The sight is disturbing and serves as evidence of the wolves' brutality and the danger they pose to Durfort's inhabitants.</p>","notes":"","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"","source":"Red Hood Iskra","category":"scenario","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","requirement":"","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"source":"Red Hood Iskra","category":"scenario","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","legacyId":"BonesPile","legacyType":"descriptor","folderName":"Red Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Montón de huesos y cadáveres","system":{"description":"<p>Una gran cueva en la guarida de los lobos llena de huesos y cadáveres humanos: los restos sombríos de las víctimas de la manada. La visión es perturbadora y sirve como evidencia de la brutalidad de los lobos y del peligro que representan para los habitantes de Durfort.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"_id":"X4HMNGa7RFZ8gEUP"}
{"name":"Secret Passageway Map","type":"storyElement","img":"icons/sundries/documents/blueprint-axe.webp","system":{"description":"<p>Knowledge of a secret passageway that connects the large dining room to the inner courtyard of the Dubois Palace. This hidden route was used by Iskra and the wolf pack to launch their surprise attack on the mansion. The passageway may also connect to the underground tunnel leading from the wolves' den to the old well in Durfort's main square.</p>","notes":"","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"","source":"Red Hood Iskra","category":"scenario","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","requirement":"","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra"},"flags":{"broken-tales":{"source":"Red Hood Iskra","category":"scenario","scenario":"Red-Hood Iskra","scenarioSlug":"red-hood-iskra","sourceDirectory":"red-hood-iskra","legacyId":"SecretPassageway","legacyType":"descriptor","folderName":"Red Hood Iskra","translations":{"es":{"name":"Mapa del pasadizo secreto","system":{"description":"<p>Información sobre un pasadizo secreto que conecta el gran comedor con el patio interior del palacio Dubois. Esta ruta oculta fue usada por Iskra y la manada de lobos para lanzar su ataque sorpresa a la mansión. El pasadizo también puede conectarse con el túnel subterráneo que lleva desde la guarida de los lobos hasta el viejo pozo de la plaza principal de Durfort.</p>","notes":"Elemento de escenario de Iskra de la Caperucita Roja.","source":"Iskra de la Caperucita Roja"}}}}},"_id":"jOMeQ0fMOa8IjG28"}
